  "detailed_description": "<strong><u>Deal with customers to get raw materials</u></strong><br> <br>Use the computer to bargain with people in the city who sell their waste to buy products cheap.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928520/extras/083e0d1811c57b92e2ba380976a6b9c9.poster.avif?t=1773839597\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928520/extras/083e0d1811c57b92e2ba380976a6b9c9.webm?t=1773839597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928520/extras/083e0d1811c57b92e2ba380976a6b9c9.mp4?t=1773839597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Collect Waste From The Places You Buy</u></strong><br><br>Collect the wastes, to gather raw matterials.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928520/extras/da5e37d07a90ea27b1599cc79adc7fdc.poster.avif?t=1773839597\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928520/extras/da5e37d07a90ea27b1599cc79adc7fdc.webm?t=1773839597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928520/extras/da5e37d07a90ea27b1599cc79adc7fdc.mp4?t=1773839597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Sort Raw Materials for Recycling</u></strong><br><br>Bring the harvested wastes to your factory and sort them by type in the sorting machine<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928520/extras/bc0934c7494927791afba3ea54e4d4e6.poster.avif?t=1773839597\" width=616 height=324 ><sourc